"{\"uid\": \"rnz.co.nz-news-olympics-2024-526967-more-paralympic-games-medals-anna-grimaldi-gets-bronze-will-stedman-wins-silver\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Anna Grimaldi celebrates winning bronze in Women's 100m - T47 Final.Photo:Ulrik Pedersen/NurPhoto/via AFP  New Zealand athletes have claimed two more medals at the Paris games with Will Stedman taking silver and Anna Grimaldi winning bronze, bringing the medal tally to five.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Grimaldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Grimaldi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Grimaldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Grimaldi\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 88, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulrik_Pedersen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ulrik Pedersen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulrik_Pedersen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulrik_Pedersen\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1045606223341979e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Grimaldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Grimaldi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Grimaldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Grimaldi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grimaldi took grabbed the bronze medal in the 100m final when the fastest qualifier, Lisbeli Marina Vera Andrade of Venezuela, slowed over the last 50m and crashed to the track.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Grimaldi\", \"score\": 0.856227705776057, \"rank\": 0.1679131303187055, \"text\": \"Grimaldi\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Grimaldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Grimaldi\"}, {\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999996794031, \"rank\": 2.2070310182183635e-10, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 393, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Venezuela\", \"score\": 0.9951741546156415, \"rank\": 0.004845120952698671, \"text\": \"Venezuela\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Venezuela\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Venezuela\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Grimaldi it represented a stunning start to her Paris 2024 campaign which includes the defence of her Long Jump title on Friday and later in the programme an appearance in the 200m.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Grimaldi\", \"score\": 0.856227705776057, \"rank\": 0.1679131303187055, \"text\": \"Grimaldi\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Grimaldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Grimaldi\"}, {\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.99099432751482e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew where I needed to put my energy into the race, I think I got a better start,\\\" she said afterwards.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would have loved another 20 metres because I think I would have caught another athlete.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The 100 metres is a race I still feel like I am finding my feet.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is scary because it is one and done and not like the long jump where you get six rounds.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, Will Stedmanwon a silver medalin the Men's 400m T36 final.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Competing a little under 16 hours after finishing fourth in the Long Jump, the 24-year-old Christchurch-based athlete produced an outstanding display to record a national record time of 52.92 behind defending champion James Turner of Australia who set a world record mark of 51.54.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beaver_and_Steve\", \"score\": 0.9999997151844987, \"rank\": 1.5125684982507867e-07, \"text\": \"James Turner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beaver_and_Steve\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beaver_and_Steve\"}, {\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9976559067313445, \"rank\": 0.001363917967980141, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"William Stedman on his way to silver in the Men's 400m T36 Final.Photo:Getty Images  For Stedman it was the fifthParalympic Gamesmedal of his career and a third successive Paralympic Games medal in the Men's 400m T36 after winning bronze medals at both the Rio 2016 and Tokyo 2020 Games.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Stedman\", \"score\": 0.9999999460383165, \"rank\": 5.391580622953432e-08, \"text\": \"William Stedman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Stedman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Stedman\"}, {\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/T36_(classification)\", \"score\": 0.5947123370588374, \"rank\": 0.6684141546527733, \"text\": \"T36\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/T36_(classification)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/T36_(classification)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He toldMorning Reporthe was definitely aiming for a sixth games in Los Angeles in 2028.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999045031, \"rank\": 8.892803993837657e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there is a lot of room to go, especially in the long jump, I think there is a lot of technical changes and perfection I can do.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously the 400, I think there is a lot of gains to be made there, today I ran a PB but I wasn't that fresh, and so, I am actually really excited for the next four years,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"score\": 0.9999999936940185, \"rank\": 6.098509565962213e-09, \"text\": \"PB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was happy with how he went in the 400m final.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got out well and felt pretty strong, I kind of hit the wall at 50m to go but managed to keep going across the line for the medal which was great.\\\"\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stedman said cerebal palsy affected his coordination and he almost tripped a couple of times in the last 50m.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were a few close calls there...\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really glad to get across the line for that silver medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Parisian crowds provided a great atmosphere to compete in, he said.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The crowd is big, but also really gets into it, they really kind of participate... today in the 400 the noise was so loud, it's so cool, it's such a good atmosphere to be competing in.\\\"\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I only got three-and-a-hours sleep last night (following the long jump final) and I was worried about that but as I warmed up, I got a good feeling,\\\" Steadman saidafter the race.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2900, \"end\": 2908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\", \"score\": 0.9970509730641026, \"rank\": 0.002957749414780629, \"text\": \"Steadman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I ran a good first half of the race and felt good around the bend and pushed it hard.\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With 50 metres to go I had nothing in the legs, I was trying to hold on and I almost tripped over a couple of times.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To run 52.92 - a 0.44 PB is crazy.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3158, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"score\": 0.9999999936940185, \"rank\": 6.098509565962213e-09, \"text\": \"PB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew I could run well today, but I did not think that well given the sleep I had.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am over the moon with that performance.\\\"\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On winning silver he said: \\\"It means a lot to me, especially as a lot of other athletes in the field ran well today.\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to run well to get the silver.\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year I have improved my 400m PB by quite a bit.\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3487, \"end\": 3489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"score\": 0.9999999936940185, \"rank\": 6.098509565962213e-09, \"text\": \"PB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is cool to see the hard work I have put in over the past three years pay off.\\\"\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steadman, who competes in the Men's 100m T36 on Saturday, said he plans to celebrate by eating some ice cream in the Village today and then rest up ahead of his final event at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3589, \"end\": 3597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\", \"score\": 0.9970509730641026, \"rank\": 0.002957749414780629, \"text\": \"Steadman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\"}, {\"begin\": 3765, \"end\": 3775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.99099432751482e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really looking forward to the 100m.\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am in really good shape, we will give it a go and then see what happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the 100m was his \\\"secondary event\\\" but he hoped to make the final and make the most of his current good form and speed.\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 4024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand  In a field loaded with experience, Stedman - who won silver in Tokyo - came agonisingly close.\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4042, \"end\": 4059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.930516750308068, \"rank\": 0.07467168072895125, \"text\": \"Radio New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}, {\"begin\": 4124, \"end\": 4129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7409734035100023, \"rank\": 0.3495756592673774, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It brings Zealand's medal tally to three, adding to cyclist Anna Taylor's silver.\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4217, \"end\": 4228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Taylor_(writer)\", \"score\": 0.9999955242206061, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Taylor_(writer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Taylor_(writer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As long as I am healthy and baby's healthy, I knew I could compete,\\\" Jodie Grinham says.\", \"from\": 4240, \"to\": 4329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4310, \"end\": 4323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Grinham\", \"score\": 0.9999980121030353, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jodie Grinham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Grinham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Grinham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Danielle Aitchison clocked 28.21 seconds at Stade de France, qualifying fastest for tonight's final.\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4331, \"end\": 4349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Aitchison\", \"score\": 0.9999986653342414, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danielle Aitchison\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Aitchison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Aitchison\"}, {\"begin\": 4375, \"end\": 4390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"for ad-free news and current affairs  Olympics 2024 RSS  Follow RNZ News\", \"from\": 4433, \"to\": 4505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4485, \"end\": 4488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 0.993547677109957, \"rank\": 0.006490747310081204, \"text\": \"RSS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}, {\"begin\": 4497, \"end\": 4500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}]}"